<topic id="check-for-new-versions">
  <title><?oxy_comment_start author="Steven" timestamp="20170511T093025+0300" comment="Merged content into &quot;upgrading.dita&quot;. Moved to not_used folder"?>Checking
    for New Versions of <ph keyref="product"/><?oxy_comment_end?></title>
  <body>
    <p>
      <ph keyref="product"/> checks for new versions automatically at start up. To disable this
      check, <ph conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/>, go to
        <uicontrol>Global</uicontrol>, and deselect <uicontrol>Automatic Version
        Checking</uicontrol>.</p>
    <p>To check for new versions manually, go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Help</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Check for New Versions</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
  </body>
